@TaskFlow.Api_HostAddress = https://localhost:5178

### Test 1 — Login with seeded user
POST {{TaskFlow.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "demo@taskflow.local",
  "password": "Demo@123"
}

### Test 2 — Hit /me without a token (expect 401)
GET {{TaskFlow.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/me

### Test 3 — Hit /me with token (paste token below)
GET {{TaskFlow.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Test 4 — Login with wrong password (expect 401)
POST {{TaskFlow.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "demo@taskflow.local",
  "password": "WrongPassword1!"
}